{"tid":2499700,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"網上討論的逆向思維","createTime":"2021-04-22T05:44:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T13:36:39.000Z","uid":4528,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c8d6c630ee16ea55aef6a6e049cd964a3c908271","tid":2499700,"uid":4528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T05:44:54.000Z","msg":"通常我地係網上同人討論啲野<br />\n少不免會想聽下人地意見<br />\n但往往都得唔到你想討論的重點<br />\n<br />\n例如你想討論一下 1000蚊買部耳機<br />\n開個post 大家覺得1000蚊樓下有咩耳機選擇<br />\n下面的留言都係 俾得1000蚊不如加多少少買xxx<br />\n可以傾到上萬蚊的耳機都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你真係想聽1000蚊樓下有咩耳機<br />\n你應該轉一轉個問法<br />\n1000蚊樓下的耳機都係垃圾 不服來辯<br />\n咁下面就會有好多人反駁 同埋都真係1000蚊樓下<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇依種網上溝通的方式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12e31caf7b2d297d66fff9d579f68ba2655504c3","tid":2499700,"uid":294238,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T06:33:19.000Z","msg":"笑人on9嘅滿足 永遠大過 幫人解惑嘅熱情"},{"pid":"c2186c84876b210d3c114f9367ab5fc11ac42635","tid":2499700,"uid":266809,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T06:35:52.000Z","msg":"關網上咩事 不嬲現實都喺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"106aaab340f19d5d2cca91026cc111e1997db43a","tid":2499700,"uid":290080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T09:25:47.000Z","msg":"如果同意，個po就完左，係咪想咁？<br />\n係就此po完。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdf969f38187d11412464ad6343edb9773647814","tid":2499700,"uid":296664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:37:11.000Z","msg":"噉樣好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a058f699a1bb36440ced3a17d6e81f764cc20d1","tid":2499700,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:03:36.000Z","msg":"下次我又試吓咁做"},{"pid":"16eb179e17f9a3658104de38bc90b266f5d359b0","tid":2499700,"uid":47356,"like":0,"